{"tid":1546974,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你地不如唔好再出嚟啦","createTime":"2019-09-06T13:35:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T14:12:37.000Z","uid":224171,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2fb7182fbc315e312b01ff710e80b652f6f7622e","tid":1546974,"uid":224171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:35:38.000Z","msg":"次次都係等人清，跟住比人捉<br />\n<br />\n警察睇撚死你班人唔敢打佢唔敢沖<br />\n警察睇撚死你班人唔敢打佢唔敢沖<br />\n警察睇撚死你班人唔敢打佢唔敢沖<br />\n<br />\n當你班友好似蚊咁拍咁<br />\n<br />\n喺前面擺哂傘陣，啲速龍出哂嚟咪又係走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果係想咁既，你覺得咁落去係辦法，我冇野好講。<br />\n<br />\n一係就玩暗殺，要掟彈既一係快過佢一步，喺佢地落車組隊前掟入架車到一把火燒。<br />\n<br />\n而加佢地攞正牌用暴力然後叫你唔好用暴力呀！"},{"pid":"9986d898ae11b2dae2fd457ce76a07d3a04b5399","tid":1546974,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:36:11.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7541798f493068005e088d11ba9a36cc6ec72ed2","tid":1546974,"uid":36994,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:36:29.000Z","msg":"咁你黎出囉 睇你表演"},{"pid":"a644155b710c18a7252e6ff9b3355388aa911514","tid":1546974,"uid":119135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:39:19.000Z","msg":"俾D差佬練靶"},{"pid":"42926fef4892d11965ea54dde29277cd6ba12de1","tid":1546974,"uid":148262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:40:54.000Z","msg":"大家可以一齊認真討論下"},{"pid":"9232cf72984c11d5ebf5f4217ad0640307e771ff","tid":1546974,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-0